{"tid":1358132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家無人唔比內拆人祠堂燒人村 重點係唔好727做 727重點和理非 撚班警黑","createTime":"2019-07-24T01:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T01:28:09.000Z","uid":220864,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4f92f82ffb0fdaf388fb857294bbad3996970ed2","tid":1358132,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:03:21.000Z","msg":"你拆人祠堂燒人村呢d野洗唔洗幾十萬人一齊做先?<br />\n起個火係咪要幾十萬人吹起佢先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">不建議任何人做犯法事情</span></span><br />\n何妖個老母都無聲無息比人做低左<br />\n唔好令一班和理非支持勇武嘅人的安全受到威脅先<br />\n佢地支持我地勇武<br />\n但係我地都要確保佢地安全<br />\n有d野唔係愈多人做愈好<br />\n勇武要和理非cover都唔係呢d時候<br />\n面對黑警就話cover有用姐<br />\n面對黑社會佢真係可以係人都打係人都劈<br />\n所以727真係保護為主<br />\n唔好因為自己的復仇情緒<br />\n危害到身邊嘅戰友<br />\n你係人群之中掉個火出去<br />\n班黑社會之後見人就斬<br />\n你想見到咁嘅情況咩?"},{"pid":"017ebc2ecbd1afb18aae973cd242dbf52eb45e61","tid":1358132,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:03:55.000Z","msg":"仆街標題打錯字"},{"pid":"cdf2297e347d729ebda9f8cf22b94bcd04fd4e58","tid":1358132,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"找"},{"pid":"40e1f655373277c016d84ad2787a2a8030c74c80","tid":1358132,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:05:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dd35643b0b12c8afabb9c80a6690824a54a45aa","tid":1358132,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:05:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"880dd1180088c9480afd33d2e24160743a2d6036","tid":1358132,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:06:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2138b9b381c34195fc6f6ded5145c0c7eeaff2f2","tid":1358132,"uid":35342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:06:22.000Z","msg":"我反而驚727有啲村突然自焚入哂我地數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2670d66cafcead6dd488a5f73c1c7a15482e61","tid":135813